The Darkest Internet Cult You’ve Never Heard Of | 764

For the past 3 months I’ve been digging into an online cult named 764. What I originally thought was just another group of weirdos quickly turned into a rabbit hole full of some of the most evil I have ever witnessed on the internet. There’s so much going on with this cult and yet so little is actually known about them, so today we’ll be digging into everything from beginning to now about the darkest internet cult you’ve never heard of.
